Html:
You can set the selected source for the tab control:<br />
<pre><code>&lt;mui:ModernTab SelectedSource=&quot;Pages/MyPage.xaml&quot; Layout=&quot;Tab&quot;&gt;
            &lt;mui:ModernTab.Links&gt;
                &lt;mui:Link DisplayName=&quot;My Link&quot; Source=&quot;Pages/MyPage.xaml&quot;/&gt;
            &lt;/mui:ModernTab.Links&gt;
&lt;/mui:ModernTab&gt;</code></pre>

See Pages/LayoutTab.xaml in the FirstFloor.ModernUI.App demo project as well.<br />
